<section class="about section" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about__grid">
      <div class="about__content">
        <p class="section-label">About Us</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Healing Through Sound & Vibration</h2>
        <p class="about__text">
          Vibe & Thrive was founded with a simple mission: to bring the proven benefits of
          Vibroacoustic Therapy to the Portland-Tigard community. We believe that healing
          doesn't have to be invasive or complicated — sometimes, all your body needs is the
          right frequency.
        </p>
        <p class="about__text">
          Our team is trained in the latest vibroacoustic techniques, combining clinical
          knowledge with genuine care for each client's well-being. Whether you're dealing
          with chronic pain, recovering from injury, or simply looking for a deeper sense of
          relaxation, we're here to help you find your balance.
        </p>
        <p class="about__text">
          Located in our new Tigard space, we've created an environment designed for comfort
          and healing — a place where you can truly disconnect, reset, and thrive.
        </p>
        <div class="about__stats">
          <div class="about__stat">
            <span class="about__stat-num">500+</span>
            <span class="about__stat-label">Sessions Delivered</span>
          </div>
          <div class="about__stat">
            <span class="about__stat-num">98%</span>
            <span class="about__stat-label">Client Satisfaction</span>
          </div>
          <div class="about__stat">
            <span class="about__stat-num">5.0</span>
            <span class="about__stat-label">Google Rating</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about__visual">
        <div class="about__image-placeholder glass">
          <div class="about__placeholder-inner">
            <span class="about__placeholder-icon">~</span>
            <p>Team / Studio Photo</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about__text {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .about__stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-gray-100);
  }

  .about__stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .about__stat-num {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-teal);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .about__stat-label {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-400);
    margin-top: 0.125rem;
  }

  .about__visual {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .about__image-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 450px;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .about__placeholder-inner {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-gray-400);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }

  .about__placeholder-icon {
    display: block;
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: var(--color-teal-light);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .about__stats {
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .about__visual {
      order: -1;
    }

    .about__image-placeholder {
      aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
    }
  }
</style>
